Package com.alibaba.ttl

Class TtlRecursiveAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.concurrent.ForkJoinTask<Void>
      • com.alibaba.ttl.TtlRecursiveAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TtlEnhanced, Serializable, Future<Void>
    public abstract class TtlRecursiveAction
extends ForkJoinTask<Void>
implements TtlEnhanced
    A recursive resultless ForkJoinTask enhanced by TransmittableThreadLocal.

    Recommend to use TtlAgent; Specially for Java 8 Stream and CompletableFuture, these async task are executed by ForkJoinPool via ForkJoinTask at the bottom.

    Since:
    2.4.0
    Author:
    LNAmp
    See Also:
    RecursiveAction, TtlForkJoinPoolHelper, TtlAgent, Serialized Form
